(k+1)!
\begin{align*} \Big(\color{blue}{(k+1)!}\color{red}{-1}\Big)+(k+1)(k+1)!&=\color{blue}{(k+1)!}+(k+1)(k+1)!\color{red}{-1}\\ &=(k+1)!\Big(1+(k+1)\Big)-1\\ &=(k+1)!(k+2)-1\\ &=(k+2)!-1\;, \end{align*}
(k+2)!=(k+2)\Big((k+1)(k)\ldots(2)(1)\Big)=(k+2)(k+1)!\;.
(k+1)! - 1 + (k+1)(k + 1)!
=(k+1)!-1+k(k+1)!+(k+1)!
=(k+1)!-1+(k+2)!+(k+1)!
=(k+2)!-1
